These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
House: modern, cape-cod, ranch-style, craftsman, palace
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, siglo, bongani, dunhill, bluemaster
5 different pets are kept: frog, hamster, horse, rabbit, snake
The people use 5 different means of transport: snowmobile, roller, car, ship, taxi
 1. the person driving the car is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is the palace house##1
 3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the aristoff-smoker##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is the dunhill-smoker##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is the cape-cod house##1
 7. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the siglo-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the modern house is on the right of the siglo-smoker##1
10. the craftsman house is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
11. the owner of the hamster is the person driving the snowmobile##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| House         | cape-cod  | modern    | craftsman | ranch-style    | palace  |
| Cigar   | siglo  | aristoff | bongani | dunhill | bluemaster  |
| Pet           | frog     | snake     | rabbit  | hamster   | horse    |
| Transport         | car | ship    | roller | snowmobile  | taxi |

