.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, rock-climbing, reading, puzzles, hiking
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, dannemann, bluemaster, game, baccarat
City: boston, rome, colone, venice, miami
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the game-smoker is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the person traveling to colone is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to miami is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
 7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the person who's hobby is reading is the person traveling to colone##1
 9. the russian is the person who's hobby is reading##1
10. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the person who's hobby is reading is the dannemann-smoker##1
13. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Hobby          | reading        | hiking | rock-climbing     | puzzles      | dancing  |
| Cigar           | dannemann   | bluemaster | baccarat    | game | havana |
| City   | colone | venice     | miami | boston    | rome  |
| Nationality   | russian     | indonesian | argentine    | spanish      | mexican    |

