The people prefer 5 different music-genres: salsa, metal, disco, d&b, classical
There are 5 different nationalities: australian, dutch, egyptian, german, spanish
The people have 5 different jobs:  videographer, architect, police-officer, analyst, entrepreneur
 1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the spanish##1
 2. the fan of salsa is on the right of the fan of disco##1
 3. the australian is in the middle##1
 4. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
 5. the egyptian is on the far right##1
 6. the fan of metal is on the far left##1
 7. the analyst is on the right of the architect##1
 8. the egyptian is on the right of the german##1
 9. the entrepreneur is in the middle##1
10. the police-officer is on the right of the dutch##1
11. the egyptian is the fan of salsa##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing go##1
13. the person playing snooker is the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Game      | snooker          | mah-jongg  | chess       | go     | monopoly      |
| Music-Genre         | metal | classical | d&b  | disco   | salsa    |
| Nationality   | dutch        | spanish | australian | german    | egyptian   |
| Job     | videographer   | police-officer | entrepreneur      | architect | analyst |

