.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: march, january, july, october, may
5 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, snooker, canasta, poker
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: country, gospel, indie, pop, techno
5 different pets are kept: lizard, cat, pony, hamster, turtle
 1. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 3. the fan of gospel is the person playing scrabble##1
 4. the fan of country is the person playing backgammon##1
 5. the person playing snooker is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is in the middle##1
 9. the fan of pop is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
10. the person who's birthday is in may is the fan of indie##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in may##1
12. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the fan of techno##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Birthday          | october        | march       | july | january   | may  |
| Game   | poker | snooker | scrabble | backgammon   | canasta |
