 2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far right##1
 4. the person drinking water is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 7. the person drinking water is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the person who's birthday is in june##1
 9. the palace house is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
11. the wooden house is in the middle##1
12. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
