The people have 5 different jobs:  security-guard, architect, musician, pilot, freelancer
City: san-francisco, new-york, london, nizza, boston
 1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the freelancer##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
 3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the security-guard##1
 4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the architect##1
 5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 7. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 8. the security-guard is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1
11. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
12. the person watching romance movies is the pilot##1
13. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Birthday      | may      | march       | october         | july  | november |
| Movie-Genre   | romance  | scientific | martial-arts | crime  | western  |
| Job   | pilot    | architect    | security-guard        | freelancer | musician     |
| City           | new-york | london      | san-francisco       | nizza   | boston   |

