.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lilac, chestnut, amber, light-blue
There 5 different types of food: orange, nectarine, pomegranate, radish, kale
5 different pets are kept: bird, dog, fish, hamster, turtle
The people have 5 different hobbies: board-games, card-games, writing, filmmaking, fishing
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
 2. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 7. the person who likes lilac is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 8. the person who likes chestnut is the person eating nectarine##1
 9. the owner of the dog is in the middle##1
10. the owner of the bird is the person eating kale##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person eating radish##1
12. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
13. the person who likes amber is the person eating kale##1

