 7. the person drinking milk is on the left of the prince-smoker##1
 8. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
10. the dutch is on the right of the indian##1
11. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
