 6. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 7. the person who growsrose is the british##1
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person who likes coral##1
 9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
10. the person who likes coral is on the far left##1
11. the person who growssunflower is on the far right##1
12. the person who growsmarigold is in the middle##1
13. the argentine is the person who likes white##1
14. the polish is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
